high_descs: turn around and walk forwards to the kitchen sink
grab the black and spotted plate out from inside of the sink
turn around and walk until you reach the fridge on your left, then turn to face the fridge and approach it
place the plate inside of the fridge to cool, then take it back out once it has cooled
turn left and walk back over to the sink
place the plate inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooled plate in the sink

high_descs: Turn around, then go straight towards the sink.
Pick up the plate in the sink.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the plate inside the fridge.
Turn around, then turn right, and go to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and head to the sink
Pick up the plate on the sink
Turn around, walk across the room then turn to your left
Open the fridge put the plate inside the fridge beside the cabbage then close the door
Open the fridge, get the plate, turn to your left then head to the sink
Put the plate on the sink
anns.task_desc: Get the plate in the fridge going to the sink
